  npcName: Piiche
  npcPortrait: {fileID: 2375522674181353051, guid: 8999911833985f94d85126b72716de8f, type: 3}
  dialogueLines:
  - Aho!
  - Wait...you can see me?
  - 
  - Howah! I thought I was fading.
  - 
  - Oh.
  - I wonder... wait, where are the other humans?
  - 
  - Just like the other manitou... I knew it.
  - 
  - I know how to help!
  - 'But I can''t interact with the human world. Not like this. '
  - You can though! Don't worry. It's a job for a berry picker likeyou.
  - 'If you can get a ground-grown Heart Berry, I can bring everyone back. '
  - 
  - Yup. from the ground. You ever been?
  - 
  - A berry picker who'se never been to the ground...
  - 'Well. No matter. There''s no one else. '
  - 'Go to the ground and come back with a Heart Berry.  '
  - 'I believe in you! '
  - 
  - If you don't bring back a Heart Berry, I won't be able to help you.
  - Elevators bring people down, right?
  - 
  - You did it!
  - 
